    "body": "### Problem\n\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/97107165/211538952-56840179-71b5-452e-828c-fc77a445a1e5.png)\r\n\r\nI would like to know if we can customize line 84's fold ending char, this may be cool!!!\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nlike this :\r\n```\r\n|\r\n|\r\n|\r\n|\r\n|\r\nL\r\n```",
